# @FUNCTION: add_qt_dep
# @USAGE: <package name> [USE flags] [minimum version] [slot + operator]
# @DESCRIPTION:
# Create proper dependency for dev-qt/ dependencies.
# This takes 1 to 4 arguments. The first being the package name, the optional
